        <span class="last-updated"><i class="bi bi-calendar-event"></i> Last updated: November 10, 2025</span>

                <div class="highlight-box"><p><strong>Important:</strong> Auto ISP Billing is a software-as-a-service (SaaS) platform. As a digital service, refunds are handled differently than physical products. Please read this policy carefully before subscribing.</p></div>

                <div class="stat-row">
                    <div class="stat-pill"><div class="big">14 days</div><div class="small">Free trial</div></div>
                    <div class="stat-pill"><div class="big">30 days</div><div class="small">Money-back guarantee</div></div>
